	<Title>
		Multiple sclerosis: Can it cause seizures?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Seizures occur more often in people with multiple sclerosis than in the general population.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Is there any connection between multiple sclerosis and epilepsy?
	</Question>
